(Dahil alam ko ang kasaysayan, tanga ka.)

00:01:30.590 --> 00:01:31.830
Ito ang Mandate of Heaven.

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.520
Masasabi ko lang kay Duke.

00:01:33.610 --> 00:01:35.090
Pangasiwaan lang ang pangangasiwa ng kabayo

00:01:35.150 --> 00:01:36.820
at buhatin ang pagkakakulong ng Duke.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:38.090
Ano pa ba ang dapat ikatakot?

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:38.990
Pero

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.790
kung nabigo kang gawin ito,

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:43.650
masisira tayong lahat.

