Sige.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:49.070
May isang kondisyon ako.

00:01:49.070 --> 00:01:49.910
Magsalita.

00:01:50.150 --> 00:01:51.120
Kapag naayos na,

00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:53.500
Kailangan kong makita agad ang Duke.

00:01:54.310 --> 00:01:55.150
Deal.

00:01:55.490 --> 00:01:56.430
(Napakapaniwala.)

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.600
Pagkatapos mo.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:01:59.600
(Hindi pamilyar ang mukha.)

00:01:59.740 --> 00:02:00.680
(Madaling umindayog.)

00:02:00.800 --> 00:02:01.640
(Hindi masama sa lahat.)

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:02.790
(Isang magandang stand-in.)

